rows.label: tlk004001_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Why...
I had only the best interests of the
state at heart...

rows.label: tlk004001_02_msg0002
rows.name: Was what I was doing so wrong?

rows.label: tlk004001_02_msg0003
rows.name:
What was I supposed to have done to
defend my country? Our Divine Beast does
not have many years left on the clock...

rows.label: tlk004001_02_msg0004
rows.name:
...Never mind. It's not as if dwelling on
it now is going to do us any good.

rows.label: tlk004001_02_msg0005
rows.name:
When I return to Superbia, I wonder
what is to become of my place within
the Senate...
